a.title: Edit section: Interpretation of the colors

tr.td: The Hashemite dynasty, bloody struggle for freedom.
The Umayyad dynasty, bright and peaceful future.
The Fatimid dynasty, the takbīr (the phrase Allahu akbar, meaning "God is great" in Arabic)
